                                                              <<center>>=== //**__How to use:__**// ===<</center>>
====== Commands: ======
//Download the plugin to see how it works!//
*  hg:
** reload
* hgarena:
** info <name>
** new <name> <limit>
* hgaedit <name>:
** limit <double>
** addgm <player>
**  addtrib <player> 
** removegm <player>
** removetrib <player>
*  hggame:
** start <arena> <int countdown>
** stop <arena>
* spawnccp
\\<<color white>>_<</color>>\\
